name: Dubio Veritas
description: This piece is a collaboration between @adhoc.orquestra (Original Music - Improvised and recorded live by Bernardo Bauer; Daniel Tamietti; Matheus Felix; P.C. Guimarães; Yuri Vellasco; Vinícius Mendes; Conducted by Guilherme Peluci); @a.i.gardening (AI + Deeplearning) and @jane.le.besque (original visual art - watercolours). Made specially for the 2nd OBJKT4OBJKT. 50/50 free objects.
